{"tid":999483,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我的賭博日記 (1)","createTime":"2019-01-28T17:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T06:58:14.000Z","uid":123335,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0051d0545fa653be2743bf3a6ba07cee78cc799b","tid":999483,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T17:25:18.000Z","msg":"我個名叫阿彪。<br />\n我讀書唔成，職業係做運輸，藍領階層。<br />\n今年二十八歲。<br />\n<br />\n我有個夢想<br />\n我要脫貧。<br />\n我唔甘心每個月只賺得果萬幾蚊。<br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n我要掙扎！<br />\n夢想係要靠自己爭取！<br />\n<br />\n我份人冇咩叻<br />\n最叻就係夠喪，夠癲。<br />\n別稱喪彪。<br />\n<br />\n岩岩見到足智彩3:00am 有場葡萄牙超級聯賽<br />\n主場嘅摩里倫斯好似幾有睇頭 <br />\n<br />\n講咁多做咩？<br />\n一鋪過 All in  $500 <br />\n一野轟落去！<br />\n唔需要猶豫<br />\n做人最緊要夠喪！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VAOFJZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVAOFJZ7.jpg&h=778a8115&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ad5c9182f34da9e021b1eecdf6de134125ee963","tid":999483,"uid":139322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T17:40:08.000Z","msg":"屌 彪彪同我同年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07a21cf5b727eaa4be95101d83a4d45e6955b31","tid":999483,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T17:40:42.000Z","msg":"屌 彪彪同我同年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73469a4259c2d16796dc0d7dce9b68eca64a805","tid":999483,"uid":139322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c07a21cf5b727eaa4be95101d83a4d45e6955b31","tid":999483,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T17:40:42.000Z","msg":"屌 彪彪同我同年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T17:41:02.000Z","msg":"屌你 copy and paste<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm