e6.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F163352_dd13463df1da79fdc25e7cc0917d5a12-1024x791.jpg&h=03f758da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5oDKrqK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5oDKrqK.png&h=894ad7d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a65a8c508707530fad744781f37bcc772ff09985","tid":999483,"uid":190066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T19:08:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ff3a0ba5fa400c4ff7b8a87556d93716d38b94a","tid":999483,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T19:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7d6a6fcc80d5df71a2dfc595683819d316d9a5","tid":999483,"uid":209786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T20:04:50.000Z","msg":"中"},{"pid":"5a790acfec994eb12a67d170a2e7dbb0e0c2f440","tid":999483,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T23:04:29.000Z","msg":"易到"},{"pid":"1a19f6acfd1df5e73f44bbadbbd52638c8490688","tid":999483,"uid":123335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:11:48.000Z","msg":"朝早去左吉野家食早餐 <br />\n點左個 &lsquo;煎雞海苔芝士飯(細)&rsquo; 配熱咖啡 <br />\n售$22 , 以我既經濟能力輕鬆 handle <br />\n<br />\n用餐期間, 我拿出手機<br />\n望望琴晚葡超既賽果：<br />\n「嗯, 果然贏錢, 一如我所料 」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/do2OV98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdo2OV98.jpg&h=345e367d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好可惜只係贏半，只賺得 $230 <br />\n距離我的脫貧夢仍有一大段距離 <br />\n仍需努力 <br />\n為夢想而活著 !! <br />\n<br />\n然後, 我就返公司停車場5/F 拎我專用銀鋁色 Toyota Hiace 烈火戰車 <br />\n開始今日運輸既勞動性工作"},{"pid":"35fbabcec11ac3a90bbee0da7f03edb8b4531d5c","tid":999483,"uid":79318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:13:23.000Z","msg":"嘩 以為係心事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094831623188652fa1481bb6db1d090c9648582b","tid":999483,"uid":26354,"l